title: Vote to secure your genesis traits!
body:
As you know, the first 3k minted (which is determined using an API that pulls from the mint transactions from the smart contract) will have a "Genesis V1" trait that adds a +5% hashrate bonus. The next 1k (those minted between 3-4k) are going to contain the "Genesis V2" trait. Genesis V2 does not have a hashrate bonus, but they are still from the genesis collection. This means they receive airdropped upgrades from subsequent collections to increase their hashrate as our facility grows. All genesis miners will have a significantly higher hashrate than subsequent collections.

Does not matter which choice you pick. 48 hours to vote, thank you!
